hivien.net/Ung-D%E1%BB%A5-Chi/Li%E1%BB%85u-nh%E1%BB%A9/poem-BbnK9B8MO57FQfjCiMCCgQ">Liễu nhứ - 柳絮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ung-D%E1%BB%A5-Chi/author-_UPCVEM67KLquJgu06Mwrw">Ung Dụ Chi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/Long-H%E1%BB%93-ngo%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BB%87nh/poem-pbmLUR7-RVDz8uEJR8krvw">Long Hồ ngoạ bệnh - 龍湖臥病</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-C%C6%B0-Trinh/author-t4xvjEQCpJQuGs7GtUeU9A">Nguyễn Cư Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/Nguy%E1%BB%87t-trung-qu%E1%BA%BF/poem-VCu73stuuBRY2j56xXxr0w">Nguyệt trung quế - 月中桂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/author-jcnyctA2yI9a8upP-Bt9aw">Nguyễn Sưởng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhung-D%E1%BB%A5c/Qu%E1%BA%BF-Ch%C3%A2u-l%E1%BA%A1p-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-lnsWsSE-qVnu018IN7tdiA">Quế Châu lạp dạ - 桂州臘夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhung-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-lGQuf2FjmcyE81PnImQFVA">Nhung Dục</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
